CVE.summary: Multiple SQL injection vulnerabilities in Superfreaker Studios UPublisher 1.0 allow remote attackers to execute arbitrary SQL commands via unspecified vectors in (a) sendarticle.asp and (b) printarticle.asp, and the ID parameter to (c) index.asp and (d) preferences.asp, different vectors than CVE-2006-5888.
